<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Meal History - HealthyLife</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/style.css" />
    <style>
        /* הוספת תמונת רקע לכל הדף */
        body {
            background-image: url('images/maz.png'); /* התמונה שלך */
            background-size: cover; /* מאפשר לתמונהnnn למלא את כל הדף */
            background-repeat: no-repeat; /* תמונה אחת בלבד */
            background-position: center center; /* ממקם את התמונה במרכז */
            background-attachment: fixed; /* התמונה נשארת במקום גם עם גלילה */
        }

        #content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px;
            color: #666;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); /* רקע לבן שקוף מעט לאיזור התוכן */
            border-radius: 8px; /* מעגלים פינות */
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 42px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-weight: normal;
            text-align: center;
        }

        #content p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .filter-form {
            background: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.7); /* רקע אפור שקוף */
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .form-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .form-group {
            flex: 1;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        input[type="date"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        select {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            background: white;
        }

        .submit-button {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: #fc8181;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 24px;
            height: 38px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 200px;
        }

        .meal-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 30px 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); /* רקע לבן שקוף */
        }

        .meal-table th {
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: left;
            color: #666;
            font-weight: normal;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            background: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.7); /* רקע אפור שקוף */
        }

        .meal-table td {
            padding: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); /* רקע לבן שקוף */
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .form-row {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .submit-button {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="page">
        <%- include('../partials/header') %>
        <div id="content">
            <div>
                <h1>Meal History</h1>
                <p>Welcome to your Meal History page! Here you can view a record of the meals you've consumed over time, including details about calories and sugar levels.</p>
                <p>Keeping track of your meals helps you maintain a balanced diet. We make it easy for you to stay on top of your nutrition!</p>
                
                <form action="/meal-history" method="GET" class="filter-form">
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="start-date">Start Date:</label>
                            <input type="date" id="start-date" name="startDate" required placeholder="mm/dd/yyyy">
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="end-date">End Date:</label>
                            <input type="date" id="end-date" name="endDate" required placeholder="mm/dd/yyyy">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="meal-type">Meal Type:</label>
                            <select id="meal-type" name="mealType">
                                <option value="all">All</option>
                                <option value="breakfast">Breakfast</option>
                                <option value="lunch">Lunch</option>
                                <option value="dinner">Dinner</option>
                                <option value="snack">Snack</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <input type="submit" value="View History" class="submit-button">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>

                <table class="meal-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Date</th>
                            <th>Meal Name</th>
                            <th>Type</th>
                            <th>Calories</th>
                            <th>Sugar Level (after 2 hours)</th>
                            <th>Day Type (Weekday/Holiday)</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <!-- Data will be dynamically generated here -->
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <p>If you have any further questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out. We are here for you!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
    </div>  
</body>
</html>
